		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Coleco Tabletop Arcade DIY Perma Power</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I would <em>not</em> assume that the A/C-to-battery adapter is purely a shape change without being able to look at the schematic of the Tabletop Arcade itself. i.e. I wouldn't assume 9VDC would be safe.

		

		</td>
